#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/Tutorial/Functions2.md:202
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Most of these should be self-explanatory. Note, however, that\n"
"in several cases (`Email`, `Artist`, `Password`) we wrap a\n"
"single value in a new record type. Of course, we *could* have\n"
