msgstr "``0`` ，表示变量在运行时被 *擦除*"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: ../src/Tutorial/Functions2.md:598
#, fuzzy
msgid "`1`, meaning that the variable is used *exactly once* at runtime."
msgstr "``1`` ，表示变量在运行时 *正好使用一次*"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/Tutorial/Functions2.md:598
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
