#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/Tutorial/Functions2.md:763
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Tutorial.Functions2> :t impl_0\n"
" 0 b : Type\n"
" 0 a : Type\n"
" 0 e : Type\n"
"   fun : a -> Either e b\n"
"------------------------------\n"
"impl_0 : Either e (List b)\n"
